{"tid":108570,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"今日有無去同人活動?","createTime":"2017-02-05T10:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T01:55:54.000Z","uid":29696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40f9860de3e3179a9a2201a3235e7033cebd820b","tid":108570,"uid":29696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:59:46.000Z","msg":"去左PR，感覺良好，不時有廣播提醒攤主<br />\n不過都係8成精品，7, 8樓行左兩圈，1樓就咁睇下就走左<br />\n<br />\n某馬好多廣告......<br />\n<br />\n以前唔捨得走，想感受氣氛<br />\n依家反而無咩留戀<br />\n<br />\n只買左SET原創小說<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人對分流入場感到煩厭，買完飛仲要等成個鐘........<br />\n純意見/感想分享，有怪莫怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48132aebcb57d424b59e63994884eb34537bce82","tid":108570,"uid":37475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:03:31.000Z","msg":"PR爽皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33a63aa51e0b04a7e55419cffb4e0f121f82758","tid":108570,"uid":8745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:10:09.000Z","msg":"PR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有廣播幫攤主防明光社"},{"pid":"aecfba4d294d599d1d2b97caccd2eb9565b97a19","tid":108570,"uid":16511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:47:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>PR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有廣播幫攤主防明光社</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點防?<br />\n<br />\n明光社... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8557bfbd026c84fa5048a1e23d05f81a154d78f","tid":108570,"uid":29696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T11:54:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>PR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有廣播幫攤主防明光社</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點防?<br />\n<br />\n明光社... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實都只係提醒18X貨品要好好包裝；check 身份證；可拒絕出售給可疑人士；有咩事要通知大會等